      <title>Revolut 为 2023 年英国银行牌照竞标做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/revolut-readies-2023-results-in-boost-for-uk-bank-license-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在审计师签署账目后，Revolut Ltd. 正在准备 2023 年的财务业绩，这使得这家金融科技公司远远提前于 9 月的法定截止日期公布数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/revolut-readies-2023-results-in-boost-for-uk-bank-license-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 09:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟对无广告 Instagram、Facebook 发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/meta-set-for-eu-warning-over-ad-free-instagram-facebook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 因其在 Instagram 和 Facebook 上采用的无广告服务订阅模式而受到警告，在欧盟根据严格的新规则对大型科技公司的最新打击中，该公司可能面临高额罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/meta-set-for-eu-warning-over-ad-free-instagram-facebook</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 08:33:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西姆塞克表示交易税仍在实施后，土耳其股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/turkish-stocks-dive-after-simsek-says-trading-tax-still-in-play</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其财政部长穆罕默德·西姆塞克 (Mehmet Simsek) 表示正在研究对投资者股票交易利润征税的可能性，随后土耳其股市大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/turkish-stocks-dive-after-simsek-says-trading-tax-still-in-play</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 08:25:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Intesa 计划与至少 45 亿欧元贷款相关的 SRT 交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/intesa-plans-srt-deals-tied-to-at-least-4-5-billion-of-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Intesa Sanpaolo SpA 正在洽谈出售信用挂钩票据的交易，这种票据被称为重大风险转移，与至少 45 亿欧元（48 亿美元）的贷款池挂钩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/intesa-plans-srt-deals-tied-to-at-least-4-5-billion-of-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 08:20:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>空客重返 1 美元商店，这次与 Spirit 资产达成交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/airbus-returns-to-the-1-shop-this-time-with-spirit-asset-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在几乎免费收购庞巴迪公司陷入困境的 C 系列飞机项目近七年后，空中客车公司再次打折收购 — — 这次是以象征性的 1 美元价格收购 Spirit AeroSystems Inc. 出售的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/airbus-returns-to-the-1-shop-this-time-with-spirit-asset-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 08:04:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德斥资 32 亿美元收购 Preqin，进军私人数据领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/blackrock-buys-preqin-for-3-2-billion-in-private-data-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司将以 25.5 亿英镑（32 亿美元）现金收购私人资本数据库提供商 Preqin，这家全球最大的资产管理公司正加快步伐成为另类资产领域的主要参与者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/blackrock-buys-preqin-for-3-2-billion-in-private-data-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 01:35:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
