      <title>法国大选后股市、欧元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/euro-gains-on-french-voting-china-eyed-after-pmi-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政治僵局的前景推动欧洲股市周一走高，投资者推高欧元，推动法国 CAC 40 指数创下 2022 年以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/euro-gains-on-french-voting-china-eyed-after-pmi-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 22:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国股市因大选结果出炉而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/euro-ticks-up-with-le-pen-s-party-set-to-win-first-french-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟党最终以小于民意调查显示的优势获胜后，法国市场出现反弹，引发全国资产的缓解性上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/euro-ticks-up-with-le-pen-s-party-set-to-win-first-french-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 19:40:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙安通林再融资贷款，为债券销售铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/spain-s-antolin-refinances-loans-paving-way-for-bond-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，西班牙汽车零部件制造商安通林-伊劳萨集团已同意为其超过 5 亿欧元（5.36 亿美元）的银行债务进行再融资，为通过债券发售为 2026 年到期的票据进行再融资铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/spain-s-antolin-refinances-loans-paving-way-for-bond-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 15:19:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
